  "excerpt": "Located in Rio de Janeiro, a new compact leisure annex has taken shape at the site of an original Oscar Niemeyer house. Designed by firm Siqueira + Azul Arquitetura, the project was formed through the acquisition of the next-door property, resulting in an expansion of the existing residence...",
